meta.title: Old Friend Encounter*DO NOT EDIT PLZ*

ttsdata.text: I mean. I take that you would remember me dude
Um, Where are you playing at? I don't remember seeing you at all
Oh, you don't huh? Well, I'll put it this way then. You could say i'm an old friend of yours that with you and your friends from before in that chamber. Kimberly and Diesel
And what was that name of yours that was with me there?
Yep. Dude, It's literally been quite some time now when we were away from each other for a bit
Yeah, but i just noticed something. Your voice, It used to be Prashant, but now it's simon
So fun fact roger, Yes, It indeed is, that's because while the wrapper online reborn site was raided, i actually went to the goanimate hospital to get it changed
Since then, I remembered what my normal voice was, which is what you just said. So that's why my voice's simon. So have you been lately?
I don't know really, Just. Seeing an old friend like you again
I see. But anyway, i think i should be going now. So, I'll see you around kid
Do you enjoy the warm weather that it is out here? It's so peaceful
Yeah. So warm. Anyway. I'm gone
